Gikorwa mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'akarere, ariko hano turibanda ku buryo busanzwe bukoreshwa mu Rwanda. Urwarwa rukorwa hifashishijwe ibitoki n'amasaka cyangwa ibindi bihingwa nk'ibigori, ariko ibitoki ni byo bikoreshwa cyane. Dore uko urwarwa rukorwa mu buryo bw'ibanze:

1. **Gutegura ibitoki**: Ibitoki byatoranyijwe bigomba kuba byujuje ubuziranenge, bivuze ko bigomba kuba byageze igihe cyo gusarurwa kandi bitarangiritse. Ibitoki birakatwa bikavamo uduce duto, hanyuma bigashyirwa ahantu hateguye neza kugira ngo bitangire gucika (gufata).

2. **Gucika kw'ibitoki**: Ibitoki bishyirwa mu cyobo cyangwa mu kindi kintu gifite isuku kugira ngo bitangire gucika. Iki gikorwa gishobora gutwara iminsi itari mike, bitewe n'ubushyuhe bw'aho hantu. Mu gihe cyo gucika, ibitoki bitangira kuvamo umusemburo w'umwimerere uzafasha mu kuvura urwarwa.

3. **Gutegura amasaka cyangwa ibindi bihingwa**: Mu gihe ibitoki biri gucika, amasaka cyangwa ibindi bihingwa byateguwe biratunganywa. Ibi bihingwa birasukurwa, bigatunganywa, hanyuma bigatogoswa. Nyuma yo gutogosa, bihita bikamurwa kugira ngo bikuremo amazi yose ashoboka.

4. **Kuvanga no kuvura**: Ibitoki bimaze gucika neza bivanwa mu cyobo cyangwa aho byari bicitswe, hanyuma bikavangwa n'amasaka cyangwa ibindi bihingwa byatunganyijwe. Iyi mvange ishyirwa mu bikoresho byabugenewe byo kuvura, aho izahamara iminsi itandukanye bitewe n'uburyohe n'ubukana bwa alukolo urwarwa rwifuzwa kugira.

5. **Gukamura**: Nyuma y'igihe cyo kuvura, urwarwa rurakamurwa hifashishijwe uburyo butandukanye bwo kuyungurura kugira ngo hatabamo ibisigazwa by'ibitoki cyangwa amasaka.

6. **Gutunganya no kubika**: Urwarwa rumaze gukamurwa, rushobora gutunganywa kugira ngo rurusheho kuba ryiza, hanyuma rugashyirwa mu bikoresho byabugenewe kugira ngo rubikwe. Urwarwa rushobora kunyobwa rutunganyije cyangwa rukongerwamo ibindi bintu bitewe n'umuco w'akarere.

prompting_state.prompt: Kuberiki imigenzo y'abahebera ikundwa cane nabantu ba Leta?

Kirundi.text:
Imigenzo y'abahebera, canke imigenzo y'idini rya kiyahudi, igizwe n'ibikorwa bitandukanye vy'ugusenga n'imanza zihambaye zama zihimbazwa buri mwaka. Iyi migenzo ikundwa kandi igashimwa n'abantu batari bake muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'ahandi kw'isi, haba mu bayahudi no mu bantu b'ayandi madini canke imico kubera ubutumwa bwayo bw'amahoro, ukwihangana, n'ugusubiza hamwe. Muri iyi migenzo harimwo:

1. **Sabato (Shabbat)**: Ni umunsi w'ikiruhuko ufatwa buri ndwi kuva ku mugoroba wo ku wa gatanu gushika ku mugoroba wo ku wa gatandatu. Uyu munsi urangwa n'amasengesho, ugusangira n'umuryango, n'akaruhuko k'umubiri n'umutima. Sabato ifise ikibanza gikomeye mu mico y'abayahudi kandi irashimwa n'abantu benshi kubera igisobanuro cayo c'akaruhuko n'ugusubiza hamwe.

2. **Rosh Hashanah**: Ni umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushasha mu kiyahudi, uhimbazwa mu kwezi kwa mbere kw'umwaka w'abayahudi (Tishrei), uhuza abantu mu gusenga no mu birori byo kwizihiza itangira ry'umwaka mushasha.

3. **Yom Kippur**: Uyu ni umunsi mukuru w'imbabazi, aho abayahudi bafata umwanya wo kwisuzuma, gusaba imbabazi, no kwiyunga n'Imana n'abantu. Ni umunsi w'igisibo, amasengesho, n'ukwiyiriza.

4. **Hanukkah**: Ni umunsi mukuru w'amatara, uhimbazwa mu kwezi kwa Kislev/Teves, ukamara iminsi umunani. Uyu munsi mukuru urangwa n'ugucana ikimazi c'amatara canke amabuji buri mugoroba, ugusangira ibirori, n'ugukina imikino y'umuco.

5. **Purim**: Ni umunsi mukuru w'akanyamuneza n'ibirori, uhimbazwa mu kwezi kwa Adar, ukibuka ugukizwa kw'abayahudi mu gihe c'ubwami bwa Perse nk'uko vyanditswe mu gitabu ca Esiteri. Purim urangwa n'ugusoma igitabu ca Esiteri, kwambara impuzu z'ibirori, gutanga imfashanyo, n'ugusangira ibiribwa n'ibinyobwa.

6. **Pesach (Passover)**: Ni umunsi mukuru wibuka ukwikura kw'abayahudi mu buretwa bwo mu Misiri, nk'uko vyanditswe mu gitabu c'Abalewi. Pesach irangwa n'ibirori vy'umugoroba bizwi nka Seder, aho hanyobwa divayi, hakaririmbwa indirimbo z'umuco, hagasomwa inkuru y'ukwikura, kandi hakaribwa ibiribwa vyihariye vy'umunsi mukuru.

1. **Imiyoborere n'Ubutegetsi**: Imiyoborere mibi, ruswa, no kutagira demokarasi biri mu bintu bikomeye bituma igihugu kidatera imbere. Iyo abayobozi bakoresha ububasha bwabo mu nyungu zabo bwite aho gukorera abaturage, bigira ingaruka mbi ku iterambere ry'igihugu.

2. **Ubukungu**: Ubukene, ubushomeri, no kutagira ishoramari rihagije mu bikorwa remezo n'inganda bishobora gutuma igihugu kidatera imbere. Ibi bishobora guterwa n'ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa mpuzamahanga bihindagurika, umwenda ukabije, cyangwa politiki z'ubukungu zidakora neza.

3. **Uburezi n'Ubuzima**: Kutagira ishoramari rihagije mu burezi n'ubuzima bishobora kubangamira iterambere ry'igihugu. Iyo abaturage badafite ubumenyi n'ubuzima bwiza, bigora kugira uruhare mu bikorwa by'iterambere ry'igihugu.

4. **Ibikorwa remezo**: Kutagira ibikorwa remezo bihagije nk'imihanda, amashanyarazi, amazi meza, n'itumanaho rishobora kubangamira iterambere ry'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.

5. **Amakimbirane n'Umutekano Muke**: Amakimbirane, intambara, no kutagira umutekano biri mu bintu bikomeye bituma igihugu kidatera imbere. Ibi bishobora gutuma habaho impunzi, gusenyuka kw'ibikorwa remezo, no gutakaza imbaraga z'abantu n'ubukungu.

6. **Politiki Mpuzamahanga n'Ubukoloni Bw'Ubukungu**: Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bishobora guhura n'ingaruka z'ubukoloni bw'ubukungu, aho ibihugu bikize bikoresha imbaraga zabyo mu bukungu n'ubucuruzi kugira ngo bishyire mu myanya myiza, bikandamiza ibihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.

7. **Ihindagurika ry'Ibihe**: Ihindagurika ry'ibihe rishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku buhinzi n'umutekano w'ibiribwa, bityo bikagira ingaruka ku iterambere ry'igihugu.

Kugira ngo igihugu giteze imbere, ni ngombwa gukemura ibi bibazo binyuze mu miyoborere myiza, ishoramari mu bikorwa remezo, uburezi, ubuzima, no kubaka ubukungu burambye. Hari kandi kongerera imbaraga imibanire myiza n'amahanga no guharanira amahoro n'umutekano.

Kirundi.text:
The phrase "Kuberiki batanga inkwano ku muryango w'umukobwa imbere yuko uwo mukobwaenda kwabirwa" is in Kinyarwanda, a language spoken in Rwanda. The English translation is: "They will pay the bride price to the girl's family before she is married off."

In many cultures, the bride price is a payment made by the groom's family to the bride's family as a symbol of appreciation and respect for the family's role in raising their daughter. It is also seen as a way of sealing the marriage agreement between the two families. The payment can take various forms, such as money, livestock, or other valuable items.

In Rwanda, the bride price is known as "igicumbi." It is an important tradition that is still practiced today, although the amount and form of payment may vary depending on the families involved. The payment is usually made before the wedding ceremony, and it is seen as a way of honoring the bride's family and showing appreciation for their role in raising her.

The bride price is not only a cultural tradition but also has legal implications in Rwanda. Under the Rwandan Civil Code, the payment of igicumbi is recognized as a legal requirement for a valid marriage. Failure to pay the bride price can result in the marriage being declared null and void.

In recent years, there has been some debate about the relevance of the bride price tradition in modern society. Some argue that it is a patriarchal practice that objectifies women and reinforces gender inequality. Others see it as a valuable cultural tradition that strengthens family bonds and promotes social cohesion.

In any case, the bride price remains an important aspect of Rwandan culture and tradition. It is a symbol of respect and appreciation for the role of the bride's family in raising their daughter and preparing her for marriage.

1. **Ubukene:** Imiryango imwe n'imwe ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gutanga ibikoresho nkenerwa mu mashure, nka uniformes, ibitabo, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ishuri. Ibi bishobora gutuma abana bava mu ishuri kubera kutabona ibyo bakeneye ngo bakomeze kwiga.

2. **Imirimo y'Ingufu:** Mu miryango imwe n'imwe, abana bashobora gusabwa gukora imirimo y'ingufu kugira ngo bafashe imiryango yabo. Ibi bishobora kubasaba kureka ishuri kugira ngo bakore imirimo itandukanye nko guhinga, kuragira, cyangwa gukora imirimo yo mu rugo.

3. **Intambara n'Amakimbirane:** Mu bice bimwe by'isi, intambara n'amakimbirane ashobora gutuma amashuri afunga cyangwa abana bakabura umutekano wo kujya ku ishuri. Ibi bishobora gutuma abana bata ishuri.

4. **Ibibazo by'Ubuzima:** Abana bamwe bashobora guhura n'ibibazo by'ubuzima bituma batiga neza cyangwa bakabura amashuri kubera indwara zikomeye cyangwa ubumuga.

5. **Imyumvire n'Umuco:** Mu mico imwe n'imwe, kwiga kw'abakobwa ntibifatwa nk'ingenzi cyangwa se hari imyumvire ko abana bakwiye gukora imirimo yo mu rugo cyangwa gufasha imiryango yabo aho kwiga. Ibi bishobora gutuma abana, cyane cyane abakobwa, bava mu ishuri.

6. **Ibibazo byo mu Muryango:** Ibibazo nk'amatati yo mu muryango, gutandukana kw'ababyeyi, cyangwa kubura umwe mu babyeyi bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'umwana bwo gukomeza amashuri.

7. **Kutagira Amashuri Ahagije:** Mu bice bimwe, kutagira amashuri ahagije cyangwa amashuri ari kure y'aho abana batuye bishobora kubera imbogamizi ikomeye ituma abana bata ishuri.

8. **Ihohoterwa n'Ikandamizwa:** Ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, ikandamizwa, cyangwa gufatwa nabi mu nzira igana ku ishuri cyangwa mu ishuri ubwaryo, bishobora gutuma abana bumva badatekanye, bigatuma bava mu ishuri.

1. **Umubirizi (Artemisia annua)**: Uyu ni umwe mu bimera bizwiho kugira ubushobozi bwo kuvura malaria. Artemisinin, ikinyabutabire kiboneka mu mubirizi, ni ingenzi mu gukora imiti ya malaria y'ubu. 3. **Inturusu (Eucalyptus)**: Amababi y'inturusu akoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye, harimo na malaria. Abantu bakunze kuyateka mu mazi, bakanywa ayo mazi cyangwa bakayakoresha mu kuvura ibimenyetso bya malaria nko kugabanya umuriro.

4. **Umuravumba (Cinchona)**: Nubwo atari umwimerere w'akarere ka Afurika, igiti cya Cinchona, aho quinine, umuti ukomeye wa malaria, ukomoka, cyakoreshejwe mu kuvura malaria mu bihe byo hambere. Quinine yabaye umwe mu miti ya mbere yizewe mu kuvura malaria mbere y'uko haza imiti mishya.

5. **Ibindi bimera**: Hari n'ibindi bimera byinshi byakoreshwaga mu kuvura malaria n'ibimenyetso byayo, birimo nka ginger, garlic, n'ibindi, byifashishwaga mu kongerera umubiri ubudahangarwa.

1. **Gutera ivyatsi**: Iki ni igikorwa cyo gutangaza ku mugaragaro ko umusore afite umukobwa yihebeye kandi yifuza ko bazabana. Umusore atuma abantu mu muryango w'umukobwa kubamenyesha ko afite umugambi wo kumurongora.

2. **Gukwa**: Nyuma yo gutera ivyatsi, hakurikiraho igikorwa cyo gukwa. Iki ni igihe umuryango w'umusore utanga inkwano ku muryango w'umukobwa. Inkwano igizwe n'ibintu bitandukanye birimo amatungo (inka cyane cyane), amafaranga, n'ibindi bitewe n'umuco w'ako karere. Gukwa ni igikorwa gikomeye kuko gishimangira ubumwe bw'imiryango yombi.

3. **Gutwikurura**: Iki ni igikorwa cyo kwerekana umukobwa ku mugaragaro ko atakiri umukobwa ahubwo agiye kuba umugore. Umukobwa yambikwa imyambaro yihariye igaragaza ko ava mu muryango we ajya gushinga uwe.

4. **Ibirori by'ubukwe**: Nyuma y'iyi mihango yose, hakurikiraho ibirori by'ubukwe aho imiryango, inshuti, n'abaturanyi bahurira hamwe mu kwishimira uyu mubano mushya. Ibirori birimo indirimbo, imbyino, n'imivugo bya gakondo, hamwe n'ifunguro rihuriweho.

5. **Guhana impano**: Mu birori by'ubukwe, imiryango yombi ishobora guhana impano zitandukanye nk'ikimenyetso cy'ubumwe n'urukundo hagati yabo.

6. **Kwakira umugeni mu rugo rw'umugabo**: Nyuma y'ibirori, umugeni ajyanwa mu rugo rw'umugabo we, aho aba agiye gutangira ubuzima bushya nk'umugore. Hari imihango ikorwa mu kwakira umugeni, harimo no kumwinjiza mu nzu yabo nshya.

prompting_state.prompt: Umuntu afise abana iyo yitavye Imana, mu migenzo y’abarundi asezerwa gute gushika ku rubanza rwa nyuma?

Kirundi.text:
Mu migenzo y'abarundi, igihe umuntu afise abana yitavye Imana, hari intambwe zitandukanye zikurikizwa mu kumusezera no mu gutunganya ibirori vy'ukumwibuka gushika ku rubanza rwa nyuma. Izi ntambwe zirashobora gutandukana bitewe n'akarere, umuryango, n'imigenzo y'ico gice, ariko hari ibintu bimwe bimwe bikunze kugaruka mu migenzo y'abarundi. Dukurikije imigenzo ya kera n'iy'ubu, twovuga ko intambwe zikurikira zikunze gukurikizwa:

1. **Gutegura no Gushingura**: Iyo umuntu apfuye, umuryango wiwe urategura ibijanye no kumushingura. Ibi birimwo kumwambika, kumuryamika mu isandugu, no gutegura aho azoshingurwa. Abantu bo mu muryango, ababanyi, n'abagenzi baraza gufata mu nda umuryango wabuze, bakaza kandi gufasha mu gutegura ivyo kurya n'ibindi bikenewe.

2. **Ikigandaro**: Ikigandaro ni igihe co kuboroga no kwibuka uwapfuye. Muri iki gihe, abantu baririmba indirimbo z'agahinda, bagasenga, kandi bagatanga ubuhamya bwiza bwerekeye nyakwigendera. Ikigandaro gishobora kumara iminsi itari mike, bitewe n'umuryango n'imigenzo yawo.

3. **Ibirori vyo Gushingurana Iteka**: Ku munsi w'ugushingura, haba ibirori vyo gusezera nyakwigendera mu cubahiro. Ibi birori birimwo imisa (ku bakirisu) canke imigenzo y'idini riranga umuryango, hamwe n'amajambo yo guhoza no kwibuka nyakwigendera.

4. **Ibirori vy'Inyuma y'Igandaro**: Inyuma y'ugushingura, hari ibirori bikurikira mu minsi canke mu mezi ari imbere, aho umuryango ushobora gutegura "ikirori co kumukurako" canke "gutabariza", bikaba ari ibirori vyo kwibuka no guha icubahiro nyakwigendera. Muri ibi birori, abantu barasangira ibifungurwa, bakanywa, kandi bakaririmba indirimbo zitandukanye ziranga umuco.

Uburyo bwakoreshwa mu gutanga amakuru mu ntwaro ya cami mu Burundi bwari bushingiye ku muco n'uburyo bwa gakondo. Dore bimwe mu buryo bwakoreshwa:

1. **Abatimbo n'Ingoma**: Mu Burundi, ingoma zari zifise uruhara runini mu buzima bw'igihugu, harimwo no gutanga amakuru. Ingoma zakoreshwa mu gutangaza ibirori bikomeye, intsinzi mu ntambara, n'ibindi bikorwa vy'ibwami. Uburyo bw'ingoma bwari uburyo bwo gutanga ubutumwa ku bantu benshi, kuko ijwi ryazo ryashobora kumvikana ku bilometero vyinshi.

2. **Intumwa z'Ibwami**: Ibwami ryakoresha intumwa mu gutanga amakuru n'amatangazo. Abo bantu, bakunze kwitwa "abamenyesha-makuru" mu buryo bwa none, bari bafise inshingano yo kugenda bavuga amakuru y'ibwami mu bice bitandukanye by'igihugu. Bakoresha amajambo yabugenewe mu gutanga ubwo butumwa, rimwe na rimwe bakanakoresha ibimenyetso n'ibisigisigi mu gutanga ubutumwa bwihariye.

3. **Inzandiko z'Ibwami**: N'ubwo uburyo bwo kwandika no gusoma bwari butaragera ku rwego rwo hejuru nk'ubu, hariho inzandiko zakoreshwa n'ibwami mu gutanga amategeko n'amatangazo. Izindi nzira z'itumanaho rya gakondo, nka "Ibimenyetso" (ibimenyetso vyakoreshejwe mu gutanga ubutumwa), na zo zarakoreshejwe.

4. **Imvugo y'Ikirundi**: Mu gutanga amakuru, ururimi rw'Ikirundi rwari rufise uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvuga no gutanga ubutumwa. Imigani, ibisakuzo, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ururimi byakoreshwaga mu gutanga ubutumwa mu buryo bwumvikana neza n'abanyagihugu.

Uburyo bwose bwavuzwe haruguru bwari bufite akamaro ko guhuza abantu no kubamenyesha ibyemezo by'ibwami, imihango, n'ibindi bikorwa by'ingenzi byabereye mu gihugu. Uko iterambere ryagiye riza, ibi buryo byagiye bisimburwa n'ibimenyeshamakuru bisanzwe n'ubundi buryo bugezweho bwo gutanga amakuru.

Kirundi.text:
Ntahemba kugira ngo tuzi imbere n'amakuru y'amajoro yose aho abakoloni baza umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute mu Burundi, kandi hari ibintu bishasha bikaba byaragije kuko n'ibi byose bya Burundi byose bibazwa n'intambwe. Ibi bikaba bikaba byaragije kuko umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute wari wakundana n'abanyagihugu bose bashoboye guteganya umwuga n'ubutegetsi bwawo.

N'umwanda we, mugihe bahora bafashwe bakorera umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute, bahora bose bakunda bakagerageza guteganya ibitekerezo byabo bivuye mu Burundi. Iyo buri bantu bakunda bagerageza guteganya ibitekerezo byabo, aho nibyo bifashwe bakorera umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute.

N'ibintu bishasha bibonye abakoloni baza umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute mu Burundi, n'aho bashoboye guteganya umwuga n'ubutegetsi bwawo, bakaba bakorwa ibyaha n'ubutegetsi bwawo. Hari abakoloni barashinzwe n'ibitekerezo byabo bivuye mu Burundi, ariko bakaba bakora ibibazo byose byabo bivuye mu Burundi.

N'umwanda we, mugihe abakoloni baza umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute mu Burundi, harimo ibi byose bishasha byaragije kubaza. Kandi n'umwanda we, mugihe abakoloni baza umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute mu Burundi, bazaba bafite ibitekerezo byabo bivuye mu Burundi.

Kuko, abakoloni bakoraga mu Burundi kuva kuwa 1890, kugeza aho 1962, mu gihe Burundi yarabikorwa n'Ubwami bw'u Rwanda. Mu gihe kandi, abakoloni bakoraga imyanda y'umwuga wo kudandaza, kandi ntibazoza kubona imbere y'uko baza umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwa gute mu Burundi.

Kirundi.text:
Mbere y'uko abakoloni bagera mu Burundi, umwuga wo kudandaza wakorwaga mu buryo bwa gakondo. Ubu buryo bwari bushingiye ku guhanahana ibicuruzwa hagati y'abantu cyangwa imiryango, hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa barter, aho abantu batangaga ibicuruzwa cyangwa imyaka bafite bakabihinduranya n'ibyo bakeneye ariko badafite. Ubu buryo bw'ubucuruzi bwari bushingiye ku mibanire myiza y'abantu, imiryango, n'ubwoko, kandi bwakorerwaga mu masoko yabaga ateguwe mu bice bitandukanye by'igihugu.

Amasoko yabaga ari ahantu h'ingenzi mu bucuruzi bwa gakondo, aho abantu bahuriraga bakagurana ibicuruzwa. Aya masoko yashoboraga kuba ari aya buri munsi, aya buri cyumweru, cyangwa aya buri kwezi, bitewe n'umwihariko w'agace. Abantu bazanaga ibicuruzwa nk'ibihingwa, amatungo, imyenda y'ubudodo, ibikoresho byo mu rugo, n'ibindi, bakabigurana n'ibyo bakeneye.

Uretse guhanahana ibicuruzwa, hari n'ubundi buryo bwo kudandaza bwakorwaga mu Burundi bwa kera, burimo gukora ingendo mu tundi turere cyangwa ibihugu by'abaturanyi kugira ngo bagurishe cyangwa bagure ibicuruzwa. Ibi byatumaga habaho guhanahana umuco, ubumenyi, n'ibicuruzwa hagati y'abaturage b'ibihugu bitandukanye.

Ku bijyanye n'uburyo bw'imari, mu Burundi bwa kera, nta faranga ryari rihari nk'uko tuzi ubu. Ahubwo, agaciro k'ibicuruzwa kagenerwaga hashingiwe ku masezerano y'abaguzi n'abagurisha, bikaba byarashoboraga guhinduka bitewe n'ibikenewe, iboneka ry'ibicuruzwa, n'ibindi.

Mu gihe cy'ubukoloni, ubu buryo bwa gakondo bwagiye buhinduka buhoro buhoro, aho abakoloni bazanye uburyo bushya bw'ubucuruzi n'imari, birimo gukoresha amafaranga nk'igikoresho cyo guhererekanya agaciro, ibi bikaba byarahinduye cyane imikorere y'ubucuruzi mu Burundi.

Kirundi.text:
Imvura n'itaze mu Burundi ni ibicumu bimeze neza kugira isubire kugwa, kandi hari ibintu byiza bintuwe bikurikira:

1. Gutanga imyanya y'imvura kuri ibindi bintu: Gutanga imvura mu myanya y'imvura ifite imbibi z'ibindi bintu bikwiye kugirango imvura izakomeje kugwa. Ibi bikwiye byinshi byose birimo gukora ku itorero rwa Burundi, mu itorero rya Ruzizi na rya Rusizi, na mu mashyamba.
2. Kwitabira umusogorozi: Kwitabira umusogorozi aho n'iyo imvura yakomeje kugwa. Hari ibindi bintu bikwiye kuva mu mashyamba, kuva mu kabwitamo, na kuva mu ntama.
3. Kwitabira ibicumu birimo byinshi: Kwitabira ibicumu birimo byinshi byose birimo gukora kugirango imvura izakomeje kugwa. Ibi bikwiye byose birimo gukora kuri ibindi bintu, kuko ariko n'iyo imvura yakomeje kugwa.
4. Gukora imbibi z'ibindi bintu: Gukora imbibi z'ibindi bintu byose byinshi byose birimo gukora kugirango imvura izakomeje kugwa. Ibi bikwiye byose birimo gukora kuri ibindi bintu, kuko ariko n'iyo imvura yakomeje kugwa.
5. Kwitabira ibicumu birimo byose: Kwitabira ibicumu birimo byose byinshi byose birimo gukora kugirango imvura izakomeje kugwa. Ibi bikwiye byose birimo gukora kuri ibindi bintu, kuko ariko n'iyo imvura yakomeje kugwa.
6. Kwitabira imvura kuva kuri ibindi bintu: Kwitabira imvura kuva kuri ibindi bintu byose byinshi byose birimo gukora kugirango imvura izakomeje kugwa. Ibi bikwiye byose birimo gukora kuri ibindi bintu, kuko ariko n'iyo imvura yakomeje kugwa.

N'ubwo bwose buri uwo kuri aya bintu birimo gukora, imvura izakomeje kugwa mu Burundi kandi hari ibicumu birimo byose byinshi byose birimo gukora.

Kirundi.text:
Mu Burundi, kimwe n'ahandi henshi ku isi aho imvura ari ingenzi mu buhinzi n'ubuzima bwa buri munsi, abaturage bafite uburyo butandukanye bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'izuba ryinshi cyangwa imvura nke. Iyo imvura itabonetse uko bikwiye, bishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye ku musaruro w'ubuhinzi n'ubworozi, bityo bigasaba ingamba zitandukanye zo guhangana n'iki kibazo. Dore bimwe mu byakorwa:

1. **Gusenga no Gukora Imihango**: Mu muco nyarwanda n'uw'abarundi, gusenga no gukora imihango y'umuco kugira ngo imvura igwe ni kimwe mu byakorwaga kuva kera. Abaturage bashobora guteranira hamwe bagasenga cyangwa bakakora imihango yihariye isaba imvura.

2. **Gukoresha Amazi neza**: Mu gihe cy'izuba ryinshi, gukoresha amazi mu buryo bukwiye ni ingenzi. Ibi bishobora kubamo kubika amazi y'imvura mu gihe cy'imvura, gukoresha uburyo bwo kuhira imyaka bugezweho butuma amazi akoreshwa neza, no kwirinda gusesagura amazi.

3. **Guhindura Igihe cyo Guterera**: Abahinzi bashobora guhindura ibihe byo gutera imyaka yabo, bagatera mu gihe cyiza cyane cyane iyo bateganya ko imvura izaba nke. Ibi bisaba kugenzura neza ibihe by'imvura n'ubumenyi ku mihindagurikire y'ikirere.

4. **Guhinga Imyaka Ikomeye ku Izuba**: Guhitamo guhinga imyaka ishobora kwihanganira izuba ryinshi n'imvura nke ni ingenzi. Imyaka nka sorgho, millet, n'ibindi bihingwa bikomeye bishobora kwihanganira ibihe by'izuba ryinshi.

5. **Gukoresha Ubuhinzi Buvuguruye**: Gukoresha uburyo bwa kijyambere mu buhinzi, nko gukoresha imbuto zihanganira izuba ryinshi, gukoresha ifumbire y'umwimerere, no gukoresha uburyo bwo kuhira bugezweho, byose bishobora gufasha mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'imvura nke.

6. **Gukora Amaterasi y'indinganire**: Mu bice bimwe na bimwe, gukora amaterasi y'indinganire ku misozi bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya isuri no kubika amazi y'imvura, bityo bikarinda ubutaka kugira ubusharire kandi bikabufasha kubika amazi menshi.

7. **Gukoresha Amazi y'Imvura**: Gufata no kubika amazi y'imvura mu gihe cy'imvura, kugira ngo akoreshwe mu gihe cy'izuba ryinshi, ni uburyo bwiza bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'imvura nke.

Izi ngamba zose zisaba ubufatanye bw'abaturage, leta, n'imiryango mpuzamahanga mu kuzishyira mu bikorwa no kuziteza imbere, kugira ngo zitange umusaruro mwiza mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'imvura nke mu Burundi n'ahandi.

prompting_state.prompt: Ni iyihe miryango y'abahutu n'abatutsi n'abatwa igize abarundi?

Kirundi.text:
Mu Burundi, sosiyete yubakiye ku miryango migari itatu y'abaturage igizwe n'Abahutu, Abatutsi, n'Abatwa. Iyi miryango migari ifite imizi mu mateka y'igihugu kandi ifite uruhare rukomeye mu mibereho y'abanyagihugu b'Uburundi. 

1. **Abahutu**: Ni bo bagize umubare munini w'abaturage b'Uburundi, bakaba bahinga kandi bakorora. Mu mateka y'Uburundi, Abahutu bakunze kuba abahinzi, bakaba baragiye bagira uruhare rukomeye mu bukungu bw'igihugu binyuze mu buhinzi.

2. **Abatutsi**: Abatutsi ni umuryango mugari wa kabiri mu bwinshi mu Burundi. Mu mateka, Abatutsi bakunze kuba aborozi b'inka, kandi inka zafatwaga nk'ikimenyetso cy'ubukire n'icyubahiro. Mu bihe bimwe na bimwe by'amateka y'Uburundi, Abatutsi bagize uruhare runini mu butegetsi bw'igihugu.

3. **Abatwa**: Abatwa ni umuryango mugari muto mu Burundi, bakaba bagize igice gito cy'abaturage. Abatwa bakunze kuba abahigi n'ababumbyi, bakaba baragiye bahura n'ibibazo by'ivangura n'ubukene. Uruhare rwabo mu mibereho y'igihugu rwagiye rugabanuka ugereranyije n'indi miryango migari.

Ni ngombwa kumenya ko iyi miryango migari ifite amateka maremare y'ubufatanye n'ubwumvikane, ariko kandi yagiye ihura n'ibibazo by'amacakubiri n'ubwicanyi bushingiye ku moko, cyane cyane mu gihe cy'ubukoloni n'ibihe byakurikiyeho. Leta y'Uburundi n'imiryango mpuzamahanga bakomeje gukora ibishoboka byose mu guharanira ubumwe, ubwiyunge, n'iterambere rirambye ry'abaturage bose b'Uburundi, hatitawe ku muryango mugari babarizwamo.

Bazungu bari mu Burundi bashoboye kumva ibihe n'izina ry'amabara y'uburundi ririmwo n'umwaka. Kuri uyu mwaka 2022, Burundi iri ku mwaka wari mu itinamabara ryo 59. Uko ni uwo mwaka w'igituma kigizweho n'imyaka 2022-2023.

Ibihe bihe n'izina rya mabara 59 mashoboye kuba kubaho bimwe bimwe. Iyi ntara irimo ibihe bihe n'izina rya mabara 59:

1. Umuhindo (January)
2. Gashyantare (February)
3. Ukwakira (March)
4. Ukwihemuka (April)
5. Ugiyunge (May)
6. Ukwakagira (June)
7. Ugashyingo (July)
8. Umutwe w'ukwezi (August)
9. Ukwandere (September)
10. Gicurasi (October)
11. Ukuboza (November)
12. Ukubona (December)

Ni mwaka wari mu itinamabara ryo 59, uyu mwaka 2022, uko ni uwo mwaka w'igituma kigizweho n'imyaka 2022-2023, umwaka wari mu itinamabara ryo 59 w'uburundi urashoboye kuba kubaho bimwe bimwe.

2. **Bujumbura Mairie**: Ni umurwa mukuru w'ubucuruzi bw'Uburundi, ikaba yaritwaga Bujumbura gusa mbere y'uko igihugu kigira umurwa mukuru mushya wa politike i Gitega. Izina Bujumbura rikomoka ku nshinga y’ikirundi "kubura", mu buryo bwo kuvuga "kugaragara" cyangwa "kumenyekana".

3. **Bujumbura Rural**: Iherereye hafi y'umujyi wa Bujumbura, ikaba igizwe ahanini n'icyaro. Izina ryayo rituruka ku kuba ari igice cy'icyaro kiri hafi y'umujyi wa Bujumbura.

4. **Bururi**: Iherereye mu majyepfo y'Uburundi. Izina ryayo rituruka ku ijambo ry'ikirundi "kururira", risobanura "kuzamuka", bishoboka ko byerekeza ku misozi miremire y'ako gace.

5. **Cankuzo**: Iherereye mu burasirazuba bw'Uburundi. Izina ryayo rishobora kuba rifite inkomoko mu muco w'aho cyangwa mu mateka y'ako gace.

Kirundi.text: Kubera iki intara ya Bugufi yakuwe ku Burundi ikaja kuri Tanzania ni kwa sababu ya vita vya 1972. Vita hivyo vikasirisha wakazi wa Bugufi kuondoka kutoka Burundi na kuingia Tanzania. Kwa hiyo, Bugufi kuwa kama sehemu ya Tanzania ni kwa sababu ya migongo ya historia.

prompting_state.prompt: Kubera iki intara ya Bugufi yakuwe ku Burundi ikaja kuri Tanzania?

Kirundi.text:
Intara ya Bugufi (Bujumbura Rural) ntiyigeze yimurwa iva ku Burundi ijya kuri Tanzania. Ahubwo, ibyo wenda waba warumvise bishobora kuba bijyanye n'impinduka z'imipaka cyangwa ibibazo by'imipaka hagati y'ibihugu, ariko nta gikorwa cyo kwimura intara cyangwa igice cy'igihugu cyabaye. U Burundi na Tanzania ni ibihugu bibiri bitandukanye byo mu karere k'ibiyaga bigari by'Afurika, kandi buri gihugu gifite ubusugire bwacyo n'ubuyobozi bwacyo.

Mu mateka, ibihugu by'Afurika byagiye bihura n'ibibazo by'imipaka bitewe n'uko imipaka yashyizweho n'abakoloni ititaye ku miterere y'imiryango n'ubwoko bw'abanyafurika. Ibi byagiye bitera ibibazo by'imipaka hagati y'ibihugu nyuma y'ubukoloni. Ariko, nta gikorwa cyo kwimura intara cyangwa igice cy'igihugu cyabaye hagati y'u Burundi na Tanzania.

Niba hari ibibazo byihariye by'imipaka cyangwa ibindi bibazo bya politiki hagati y'u Burundi na Tanzania, ibyo bibazo bikwiye gusuzumwa mu buryo bwihariye, ariko ntibikwiye gufatwa nk'uko intara yimuriwe mu kindi gihugu. Ni ngombwa kandi kugenzura amakuru yizewe kugira ngo umuntu abone ishusho nyayo y'ibibera mu karere.

3. **Kwiga ubumenyi n'ubuhanga bwo kuyobora:** Umwana w'umwami yashoboraga koherezwa mu miryango y'abanyacyubahiro cyangwa abayobozi b'ingabo kugira ngo yige ibijyanye n'ubuyobozi, uburyo bwo kurwana, n'ubumenyi bw'iby'amategeko n'ubutabera. prompting_state.prompt: Ni koko umwana azoba umwami yavukana imbuto? Sigura igituma ari vyo canke atari vyo.

Kirundi.text:
Ico kibazo cerekeye ko umwana azoba umwami yavukana imbuto (canke atavukana zo) kirashobora gusigurwa mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'ingene umuntu yumva canke afata ibintu bijanye n'uburongozi n'ubwami. Ariko, reka tubisigure mu buryo bubiri: imvugo y'ikigereranyo n'ukuri kw'ibintu.

1. **Mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo**: Iyo bavuze ko "umwana azoba umwami yavukana imbuto," bishobora kumvikana nk'ikigereranyo kivuga ko umuntu wese agenewe kuba umuyobozi canke umwami mu buzima bwiwe bw'ejo hazoza afise ibikenewe vyose (imbuto) kuva akivuka. Ibi bishobora gusigura ingabire, ubushobozi, canke impano zidasanzwe zishobora kumufasha kuba umuyobozi mwiza. Muri uyu mwumvikano, "imbuto" zisigura ubushobozi n'impano z'umuntu, atari ivyo yavukanye mu buryo bw'umubiri gusa, ariko n'ivyo ashobora kuronka biciye mu burere, inyigisho, n'ibindi.

2. **Mu kuri kw'ibintu**: Mu bisanzwe, kuba umwami canke umuyobozi ntibisaba ko umuntu avukana imbuto zihariye mu buryo bw'umubiri canke mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Ubwami mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe buragendera ku miryango, aho umwana avuka mu muryango w'ibwami ashobora kuzoba umwami bitewe n'amategeko y'irage. Muri uyu mwumvikano, "kuvukana imbuto" ntibisigura ko afise ibintu bidasanzwe mu mubiri canke mu bwenge, ariko ko afise uburenganzira bwo kuba umwami bitewe n'uko yavutse mu muryango w'ibwami.

Mu gusozera, igisubizo ku kibazo cawe kirashobora guhinduka bitewe n'ingene umuntu afata "imbuto" umwana yavukanye nazo. Mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, birashoboka ko bavuga ko umwana azoba umwami yavukanye imbuto mu gihe afise ubushobozi n'impano zidasanzwe. Mu buryo bw'ukuri kw'ibintu, kuba umwami bivana n'amategeko y'irage n'umuco w'igihugu, atari imbuto umuntu yavukanye nazo mu buryo bw'umubiri canke bw'ikigereranyo.

Abatamvyi b'ingoma bashobora kuvuzwa ingoma kuri iki cyangwa iki kintu kimwe, kuko ni bo bakanagira ibikorwa byabo nyuma y'ingoma.

N'iyo baba bashoboye gukura ibirato imbere yo kuvuzwa ingoma, bakanakora iki cyangwa iki gitondo cyane kugira ngo bakurikije umwimerere w'abandi n'ubuzima bwabo. Icyo bakorera kandi bakanakurikira ni:

3. Gutanga amakuru amagara y'imyaka yose
4. Gutanga amakuru y'imibereho yose
5. Gutanga amakuru y'imibanire yose
6. Gushyira mu nzira imyitwarire yose
7. Kwumva ingoma beza kumva ko bakinnye, kuko bakanakoresha amakenga n'ibikorwa by'umutekano

N'iyo nabi abatamvyi b'ingoma bashoboye kuvuzwa ingoma n'ibindi bikomeye mu gihe cyane, bazaba bakoresheje imyitoro y'umutekano kugira ngo abahunga bugufi bashobore kuvuzwa ingoma n'ibindi bikomeye mu gihe cyane.

Zikoreshwa mu birori bitandukanye, harimwo n'ibirori vyo guhimbaza no kwibuka intwari z'igihugu, mu birori vy'ubugeni, mu kwimika abami, no mu bindi bihe vy'ingenzi mu buzima bw'igihugu n'umuco w'abarundi.

Kubera iyo mpamvu, abatamvyi b'ingoma, canke abavuzi b'ingoma, babanza gukura ibirato imbere yo kuvuza ingoma nk'ikimenyetso c'icubahiro n'ukwubaha ingoma nk'ikintu ceranda. Ibi bikorwa nk'uburyo bwo kwerekana ko bari mu mwanya w'ubutore n'ubusabane n'ingoma, kandi ko bari mu kibanza ceranda, aho bategerezwa kuba bafise umutima w'ubwitonzi, ubwubahane, n'ukwicisha bugufi.

Gukura ibirato kandi birerekana ko abavuzi b'ingoma bari mu mwanya w'ubwitonzi n'ubwubahane imbere y'umuco wabo, bakaba biteguye gukorana n'ingoma mu buryo bw'umwuka n'umubiri. Ni ikimenyetso c'uko bari mu kibanza ceranda kandi ko bategerezwa kugira uruhara rwabo mu kubungabunga no gukomeza umuco wabo n'akaranga kabo mu buryo bwubaha kandi bwimbitse.

Muri make, gukura ibirato imbere yo kuvuza ingoma ni ikimenyetso c'icubahiro, ukwubaha, n'ukwicisha bugufi imbere y'umuco n'akaranga k'abarundi, bikerekana kandi ko abavuzi b'ingoma bari mu mwanya w'ubutore n'ubusabane n'ingoma, nk'ikintu ceranda mu muco w'abarundi.

Kirundi.text:
Imbere y’intwaro ya cami, Uburundi bwatwarwa hakurikijwe uburyo bwa gakondo bw’ubwami. Uburundi bwari igihugu cya cyami, aho umwami, yitwaga "Umwami w’Uburundi" cyangwa "Mwami," yari ku isonga ry’ubutegetsi. Ubwami bw’Uburundi bwari bufite imizi mu muco n’imigenzo ya kera, aho umwami yafatwaga nk’umuhuza w’Imana n’abantu, akagira uruhare rukomeye mu miyoborere y’igihugu n’imibereho y’abagituye.

Umwami yari afite inshingano zo kuyobora igihugu, gucunga umutekano, no kugena amategeko agenga imibanire y’abantu n’ubutaka. Yari afite kandi uruhare mu bikorwa by’idini n’umuco, aho yashoboraga kugira uruhare mu migenzo itandukanye n’ibirori bya gakondo.

Ubwami bw’Uburundi bwagenderaga ku mitwe y’imiryango y’abatware, aho abatware b’imiryango itandukanye bagiraga uruhare mu miyoborere y’igihugu, bafasha umwami mu kuyobora no gucunga ibice bitandukanye by’igihugu. Abatware bari bafite inshingano zo gucunga umutekano, gukemura amakimbirane, no gukurikirana ibikorwa by’ubuhinzi n’ubworozi mu bice byabo.

Ubwami bw’Uburundi bwari bufite kandi inzego z’ubucamanza n’igisirikare, aho abasirikare n’abacamanza bafashaga umwami mu kubungabunga umutekano no gukemura amakimbirane.

Mu gihe cy’ubukoloni, uburyo bw’imiyoborere y’Uburundi bwahindutse cyane, aho abakoloni b’Ababiligi bafashe ubutegetsi mu 1916, bakaza kugira uruhare rukomeye mu miyoborere y’igihugu. Nyuma y’ubukoloni, Uburundi bwabonye ubwigenge mu 1962, buva ku butegetsi bwa cyami bujya mu butegetsi bwa Repubulika.

Mu gihe cy’ubutegetsi bwa cyami, Uburundi bwagize ibihe bitandukanye by’ubutegetsi bw’abami batandukanye, aho buri mwami yazanaga impinduka mu miyoborere n’imibereho y’abaturage, ariko umuco w’ubwami n’imigenzo ya gakondo bikagumaho nk’inkingi ya mwamba mu muryango nyarwanda.

2. **Gushaka umufasha mu buryo bukwiye:** Gushaka umufasha bisaba ubushishozi n'isengesho kugira ngo ubone umuntu uhuje nawe mu ntekerezo, mu myemerere, no mu ntego z'ubuzima.

3. **Kuganira ku ntego n'ibyifuzo by'urugo rwanyu:** Ni ngombwa ko umuhungu n'umukunzi we baganira ku ntego zabo, ibyifuzo, n'uko bateganya kubaho mu rugo rwabo, harimo n'ibijyanye n'imari, abana, akazi, n'ibindi.

4. **Kwitegura mu buryo bw'imari:** Kubaka urugo bisaba imari, bityo ni ngombwa gutegura ingengo y'imari y'urugo, kuzigama, no kwiga uburyo bwo gucunga neza amafaranga yanyu.

5. **Gushaka aho muzatura:** Mugomba kureba aho muzatura, haba mu nzu mukodesha cyangwa mu nzu yanyu bwite. Ni ngombwa kureba ibijyanye n'ubushobozi bwanyu bw'imari n'aho mukunda.

6. **Kwitegura mu buryo bw'umubiri n'ubuzima:** Kubaka urugo bisaba imbaraga n'ubuzima bwiza, bityo ni byiza kwita ku mibereho myiza, kurya neza, no gukora siporo.

7. **Kwiga kubana n'abandi:** Kubana n'umuntu bisaba kwiga kumvikana, kuganira, no gukemura amakimbirane mu mahoro. Ni byiza kwiga uburyo bwo kumvikana no kubaha ibitekerezo by'umufasha wawe.

8. **Gushyira imbere umuryango:** Ni ngombwa ko umuhungu ategura umutima we kuba umugabo n'umubyeyi uzita ku muryango we, akawushyira imbere mu byemezo n'ibikorwa bye.

9. **Gusenga no gushyira Imana imbere:** Mu muco nyarwanda n'indi mico, gusenga no gushyira Imana imbere mu rugo ni ingenzi. Ni byiza ko umuryango ushingira ku myemerere yabo, bagasenga kandi bagashyira Imana imbere mu rugo rwabo.

10. **Kwiga no kwitegura inshingano z'urugo:** Ni byiza kwiga no kwitegura inshingano z'urugo, harimo no kuba umubyeyi, umugabo, n'umutware w'urugo.

Ibi bishingiye ku myumvire y'icyubahiro n'ubusugire bw'ubwami, aho umwami yafatwaga nk'ikirenga mu gihugu cye, akaba umuhuza w'abaturage be n'Imana, ndetse akaba n'umurinzi w'umuco n'imigenzo y'igihugu. Hari impamvu zitandukanye zishobora gusobanura iyi myumvire:

1. **Icyubahiro n'Ubwigenge bw'Ubwami:** Umwami yafatwaga nk'umuntu uri hejuru y'abandi bose mu gihugu cye, afite ububasha n'icyubahiro bidasanzwe. Gutumira ku wundi mwami byashoboraga gufatwa nk'ikimenyetso cyo kugabanya icyo cyubahiro cyangwa kwemera ko undi mwami amuruta, ibintu bitari byemewe mu muco nyarwanda.

2. **Kwirinda Amakimbirane:** Mu bihe bya kera, ubwami bwashoboraga kuba mu makimbirane cyangwa mu buhangange n'ubundi bwami. Kutimira ku wundi mwami byari uburyo bwo kwirinda guha urwaho amakimbirane, cyangwa se kwirinda kugaragaza intege nke z'ubwami bwabo imbere y'abandi.

3. **Kubaha Imigenzo n'Imyemerere:** Mu muco nyarwanda, hariho imigenzo n'imyemerere byahaga umwami icyubahiro n'ububasha budasanzwe, birimo no kuba umuhuza hagati y'abaturage n'Imana. Gutumira ku wundi mwami byashoboraga gufatwa nk'ugusuzugura iyo migenzo n'imyemerere.

4. **Kwimakaza Ubwigenge n'Ubumwe bw'Igihugu:** Kwirinda gutumira ku wundi mwami byanafashaga mu kwimakaza ubwigenge n'ubumwe bw'igihugu, byerekana ko igihugu gifite ubushobozi bwo kwitegeka no kwihitiramo inzira yacyo itagombye kwivanga cyangwa guterwa inkunga n'ubundi bwami.

Mu gusoza, umuco nyarwanda wubaha cyane ibijyanye n'ubwami, kandi imyitwarire y'umwami yagombaga kugaragaza ubwigenge, icyubahiro, n'ububasha bw'igihugu cye. Kutimira ku wundi mwami byari bimwe mu buryo bwo kubungabunga ibyo byose.

Mu muco wa kera, abana batangura kwambara impuzu z'ibiti (cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'umwimerere nk'uruhu rw'amatungo) mu gihe bageze mu kigero cy'imyaka itandukanye bitewe n'umuco n'ibidukikije by'aho bari batuye. Nta gihe cyihariye cyangwa imyaka rusange yashyirwaho kuko ibi byahindukaga bitewe n'umuco, ikirere, n'ibikenewe by'umuryango n'umuryango mugari.

Impamvu zatumaga abana batangira kwambara impuzu z'ibiti cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'umwimerere zirimo:

1. **Kurinda umubiri:** Impuzu zatangaga uburinzi ku mubiri w'umwana mu bihe by'ikirere gikomeye, harimo ubukonje cyangwa izuba ryinshi, ndetse no kurinda uruhu rwabo ku bisimba n'ibindi bintu bishobora kubagirira nabi.

2. **Imihango y'umuco:** Mu mico imwe n'imwe, kwambara impuzu byashoboraga kuba ikimenyetso cyo kwinjira mu kindi cyiciro cy'ubuzima, nk'ubwangavu cyangwa ubugimbi. Impuzu zashoboraga kandi kugaragaza imyaka y'umwana, ubutunzi bw'umuryango, cyangwa imirimo yihariye y'umuco.

3. **Ubupfura n'isuku:** Kwambara impuzu byashoboraga kandi kugaragaza isuku n'ubupfura, bituma abana bagaragara neza kandi bakurikiza amahame y'umuco wabo.

4. **Guhindura ikirere n'ibidukikije:** Mu bice bimwe, guhinduka kw'ikirere n'ibidukikije byashoboraga gutegeka igihe n'ubwoko bw'impuzu abana batangira kwambara. Urugero, mu bice bikonja, impuzu z'uruhu rw'amatungo zashoboraga gukoreshwa kugira ngo zitange ubushyuhe, mu gihe mu bice bishyuha, impuzu zoroheje z'ibiti cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'umwimerere byashoboraga gukoreshwa kugira ngo zifashe mu kugabanya ubushyuhe.

Mu gusoza, igihe n'impamvu abana batangira kwambara impuzu z'ibiti cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'umwimerere byahindukaga cyane bitewe n'umuco, ikirere, n'ibikenewe by'umuryango. Nta myaka rusange yashyirwaho kuko ibi byose byahindukaga bitewe n'ibidukikije n'imibereho y'abantu mu bihe bya kera.

prompting_state.prompt: Kubera iki ku munsi w'umuganuro hari abantu bo mu muryango umwe bahonyorwa n'inka zishotse kunywa amazi?

Kirundi.text:
Mu muco nyarwanda, umunsi w'umuganuro wari umwe mu minsi mikuru ikomeye yizihizwaga buri mwaka mu Rwanda rwo hambere. Wari umunsi wo gushima no kuganura ibyo umuryango, umudugudu cyangwa igihugu muri rusange byagezeho mu buhinzi n'ubworozi, bityo bakishimira umusaruro wabonetse. Uyu munsi wari ugamije kandi guhuza abantu, gusangira no gusabana, aho abantu bashimiraga imana zabo n'abakurambere babo ku byiza byabaye mu mwaka ushize no gusaba umugisha mu mwaka utaha.

Ku bijyanye n'igikorwa cyo guhonyora inka zishotse kunywa amazi, ntabwo ari umuco wari uzwi cyane mu Rwanda rwo hambere nk'igice cy'umuhango w'umuganuro. Mu muco nyarwanda, inka zifite agaciro gakomeye kandi zitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye. Hari imigenzo myinshi ijyanye n'ubworozi bw'inka, harimo no kuziha amazi yo kunywa mu buryo buteguye neza, ariko ibyo guhonyora abantu n'inka zishotse kunywa amazi ntibigaragara nk'igice cy'umuco w'umuganuro cyangwa undi muco wemewe mu Rwanda.

Bishoboka ko ibyo uvuga bishobora kuba ari ibitekerezo cyangwa imigenzo y'ahandi itari igize umuco nyarwanda wemewe, cyangwa se bishobora kuba ari ugucanganyikisha imigenzo itandukanye. Mu muco nyarwanda, umuganuro wari umunsi wo kwishimira umusaruro, gusangira, no gusaba imigisha, aho gukora ibikorwa byo guhonyora cyangwa gukomeretsa.

Niba hari ibindi bisobanuro cyangwa imigenzo yihariye yabayeho mu mateka y'u Rwanda cyangwa mu bindi bihugu bijyanye n'uyu muhango, bishobora kuba bitazwi cyane cyangwa bitanditswe mu mateka azwi. Ni ngombwa gukora ubushakashatsi bwimbitse kugira ngo hamenyekane neza inkomoko n'ibisobanuro by'imigenzo nk'iyo.

Ndakubavuga ko kwishyura abaturage kwishyura abaturage kuko bavuga ko "uruvyaro rw'umuhanda ntirugero". Ibi vyose bakibakura bakaba bakurikiza gukora kuri ikinamico y'umuhari wabo. Ibi bikaba byoherereye kuko bakaba batagira ubuzima bw'abaturage. Ibibazo bijanye no kubura uruvyaro mu bashakanye birashobora kuba intandaro y'umubabaro n'umunyenga mu mibanire yabo. Ariko, hari intambwe zimwe zimwe zishobora gufatwa mu guhangana n'iki kibazo. Dore bimwe mu vyokorwa:

1. **Gushaka Inyigisho n'Ubufasha bwa Muganga:** Ni ngombwa ko abubakanye bafise ikibazo co kubura uruvyaro bashaka ubufasha bw'abahinga mu vy'ubuvuzi, harimwo abaganga b'indwara z'abagore n'abagabo, hamwe n'abahinga mu vy'ugufasha kugira uruvyaro (fertility specialists). Abo bahinga bashobora gutanga ibipimo n'isuzumwa ryimbitse kugira bamenye ico kibazo gishingiye ko, bongere batange inyishu zibereye.

2. **Kwihweza Amahitamo y'Ugufasha Kugira Uruvyaro:** Hari uburyo butandukanye bwo gufasha abubakanye kugira uruvyaro, harimwo ubuvuzi bwo gufasha mu vy'ugusama (fertility treatments) nka IVF (In Vitro Fertilization), IUI (Intrauterine Insemination), n'ibindi. Kandi hariho n'uburyo bwo gukoresha intanga z'abandi (donor sperm or eggs), gukoresha umuntu yitangira inda (surrogacy), canke gufata umwana mu mugongo (adoption).

3. **Kwiga no Kwumva Ibindi Bishoboka:** Hari igihe abubakanye bakeneye kwiga no kwumva ibindi bishoboka vy'ukugira umuryango, harimwo gufata umwana mu mugongo. Guhitamwo gufata umwana mu mugongo birashobora kuba inzira ikomeye yo kugira umuryango ku bantu bafise ikibazo co kubura uruvyaro.

4. **Gushigikirwa n'Imitima:** Kubura uruvyaro birashobora gutera umubabaro n'umunyenga. Ni ngombwa ko abubakanye bashigikirana, kandi bakaronka n'ubufasha bw'umutima biciye mu biganiro n'abahinga mu vy'inyifato n'ivyiyumviro (psychologists) canke mu matsinda yo gushigikirana.

5. **Kwitaho Amagara n'Imibereho Myiza:** Kwitaho amagara yanyu, harimwo kurya neza, gukora imyimenyerezo ngororamubiri, no kwirinda ingeso mbi nka kunywa itabi canke kunywa inzoga nyinshi, birashobora kugira ico bikoze mu kugira uruvyaro.

6. **Kwihangana no Kuguma Ufise Icizere:** Ikibazo co kubura uruvyaro gishobora kuba urugendo rurerure kandi ruruhije. Ni ngombwa kuguma ufise icizere no kwihangana, no kwibuka ko hariho inzira nyinshi zishobora gutuma mugera ku nzozi zanyu zo kugira umuryango.

Mu gihe cose, ni ngombwa ko abubakanye baganira ku vyiyumviro vyabo, ibyifuzo vyabo, n'ingene bumva bamerewe muri urwo rugendo, kugira ngo bashobore gufata ingingo zibereye hamwe.

prompting_state.prompt: Kubera iki amasaka azokoreshwa ku muganuro bayarinda kugira inyoni ntiziryemwo ishaka na rimwe kugeza bayakuye mu murima?

Kirundi.text:
Amasaka ni kimwe mu bihingwa by'ingenzi mu muco wa benshi mu baturage bo mu bihugu bya Afurika, birimo n'ibice bimwe by'u Rwanda. Kubera akamaro kayo, haba mu mirire no mu muco, amasaka agomba kwitabwaho neza kugira ngo yeze neza kandi agere ku isarura ryiza. Mu muco w'imigani n'imigenzo, amasaka afite umwanya wihariye, aho ashobora gukoreshwa mu birori bitandukanye nko mu muganuro, umuhango wo gushima imana z'uburumbuke no gusaba umusaruro mwiza mu bihe bizaza.

Kurinda amasaka kugira ngo inyoni ntizayarye mbere y'uko asarurwa, cyane cyane mu gihe cyo gutegura umuganuro, bifite impamvu zikurikira:

1. **Kubungabunga Umusaruro:** Inyoni zishobora kwangiza umusaruro munini w'amasaka mu gihe zitabujijwe. Kubera ko amasaka aba ari ingenzi mu birori by'umuganuro, abahinzi bakoresha uburyo butandukanye bwo kuyarinda kugira ngo hatazabaho igihombo cy'umusaruro.

2. **Agaciro mu Muco:** Mu muco wa benshi, amasaka afatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'uburumbuke n'umugisha. Kuyarinda rero mbere y'umuganuro ni uburyo bwo kubaha no kugirira icyubahiro imigenzo n'imiziro ijyanye n'ubuhinzi n'umusaruro.

3. **Kwitegura Umuganuro:** Umuganuro ni umuhango wo gushimira no gusangira umusaruro wavuye mu buhinzi. Amasaka, nk'igihingwa cy'ingenzi, agomba kuba yararinzwe neza kugira ngo azabashe gukoreshwa muri uyu muhango. Kubera ko umuganuro ufite akamaro kanini mu muco, birakwiye ko ibihingwa nk'amasaka birindwa by'umwihariko.

4. **Kubahiriza Imigenzo:** Hari imigenzo n'imiziro ijyanye no kurinda amasaka n'ibindi bihingwa. Uburyo bwo kubirinda bushobora kuba burimo gukoresha uburyo bwa gakondo nko guhagarika inyoni hakoreshejwe ibintu bitandukanye birimo n'imirimo y'ubugeni, gukoresha ibishishimuzo, cyangwa gucunga imirima.

Mu gusoza, kurinda amasaka kugira ngo inyoni ntizayarye mbere y'umuganuro ni uburyo bwo kubungabunga umusaruro, kubaha umuco, no kwitegura neza umuhango w'umuganuro. Ni igikorwa gifite agaciro kanini mu mibereho y'abahinzi n'umuryango mugari, kigaragaza uburyo bwo guhuza ubuhinzi n'imigenzo ya gakondo.

prompting_state.prompt: Ni kubera iki amasanganya y’imodoka ari menshi mu gihugu?

Kirundi.text:
Amasanganya y'imodoka akomeje kuba menshi mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi kubera impamvu zitandukanye. Nubwo buri gihugu gifite ibibazo byihariye bishobora kongera ibyago byo kugira impanuka, hari impamvu rusange zikunze kugaragara henshi. Dore zimwe muri zo:

1. **Ubwiyongere bw’imodoka mu mihanda**: Uko imodoka ziyongera mu mihanda, ni ko n’ibyago byo kugongana cyangwa gukora impanuka birushaho kwiyongera. Ibi bikunze kugaragara cyane mu mijyi ikomeje kwaguka no mu bihugu biri mu nzira y’amajyambere aho umubare w’abatunze imodoka ukomeje kwiyongera.

2. **Imihanda idahagije cyangwa idakorewe neza**: Imihanda mito, yangiritse, cyangwa idafite ibimenyetso bihagije bishobora gutera impanuka. Ibi bikunze kugaragara mu bihugu bifite ibikorwaremezo bidahagije cyangwa aho imihanda ititabwaho neza.

3. **Amategeko y’umuhanda adakurikizwa**: Kutubahiriza amategeko y’umuhanda, nko kutubahiriza umuvuduko ntarengwa, gukoresha telefone utwaye, cyangwa gutwara imodoka wasinze, ni zimwe mu mpamvu zikomeye zitera impanuka.

4. **Ubushobozi buke bw’abashoferi**: Abashoferi batitaweho mu mahugurwa no mu myitozo ihagije, cyangwa abatubahiriza amabwiriza y’umuhanda, bashobora kuba intandaro y’impanuka.

5. **Ibinyabiziga bitameze neza**: Imodoka zititaweho neza, zifite ibibazo bya tekiniki, nk’amatara ataka, feri zidakora neza, cyangwa amapine ashaje, zishobora guteza impanuka.

6. **Ihindagurika ry’ikirere**: Imvura nyinshi, ibihu, cyangwa ibindi bihe by’ikirere bishobora kugora abashoferi kubona neza cyangwa kugenzura imodoka zabo, bityo bikaba byatera impanuka.

7. **Ibikorwa by’ubwikorezi rusange bidahagije cyangwa bitizewe**: Mu bihugu bimwe, abantu benshi bakoresha imodoka zabo bwite kubera ko serivisi z’ubwikorezi rusange zidakora neza cyangwa zitizewe. Ibi bishobora kongera umubare w’imodoka mu mihanda no guteza akajagari.

Kugira ngo hagabanywe amasanganya y’imodoka, hakenewe ingamba zifatika zirimo kubaka no kuvugurura imihanda, gukaza amategeko y’umuhanda no kuyashyira mu bikorwa, guteza imbere ubwikorezi rusange, no gukora ubukangurambaga ku mutekano wo mu muhanda.

Kirundi.text:
Kuguma kudahinduka kw'agaciro k'amahera y'igihugu nk'Uburundi bishobora guterwa n'ibintu bitandukanye, birimwo ibibazo vy'ubutunzi bw'igihugu, politike, n'ibindi bintu bijanye n'ubudandaji mpuzamakungu. Naho atari ibintu vyose bishobora gusigurwa muri aka kanya, reka dutange insiguro zimwe zishobora kugira uruhara mu kuguma kudahinduka kw'agaciro k'amahera y'Uburundi:

1. **Ubudandaji Bw'igihugu n'Ubutunzi Buke**: Uburundi ni kimwe mu bihugu bifise ubutunzi buke kw'isi, n'ubudandaji buri hasi. Ibi bishobora gutuma ifaranga ry'igihugu ritagira inguvu ku masoko mpuzamakungu, bigatuma agaciro karyo kaguma ari gato.

2. **Ibibazo vya Politike n'Umutekano**: Ibibazo vya politike n'umutekano muke birashobora gutuma abashoramari b'abanyamahanga batinya gushora imari mu gihugu, bigatuma amahera y'igihugu aguma ata agaciro.

3. **Ubwinshi bw'Ifaranga mu Gihugu**: Iyo Leta isohora amafaranga menshi kuruta ayo ubutunzi bw'igihugu bushobora kwakira, bishobora gutuma haba ihindagurika ry'agaciro k'amafaranga, aho ifaranga ritakaza agaciro.

4. **Ubudandaji Mpuzamakungu n'Ideni Rya Hanze**: Uburundi bufise ubudandaji mpuzamakungu buto hamwe n'ideni rinini rya hanze. Ibi bishobora gutuma igihugu kigira ibibazo mu kubona amadevize (foreign currency), bikagira ingaruka ku gaciro k'amafaranga y'igihugu.

5. **Ibiciro vy'ibidandazwa ku masoko mpuzamakungu**: Igihe ibiciro vy'ibidandazwa Uburundi butumiza canke butanga hanze bihindagurika, bishobora kugira ingaruka ku gaciro k'amafaranga y'igihugu. Urugero, igihe ibiciro vy'ikawa n'icayi (ibidandazwa bikuru vy'Uburundi) bigabanutse ku masoko mpuzamakungu, bishobora kugabanya amadevize yinjira mu gihugu, bigatuma ifaranga ritakaza agaciro.

6. **Igipimo c'Inyungu**: Igipimo c'inyungu gitangwa n'ibanki nkuru y'igihugu gishobora kugira ingaruka ku gaciro k'amafaranga. Iyo igipimo c'inyungu kiri hasi cane, bishobora gutuma ifaranga ritakaza agaciro kuko abantu baba bafise akanyamuneza ko kugura no gusohora amafaranga aho kuyazigama.

Kugira ngo igihugu nk'Uburundi kibashe kuzamura agaciro k'amafaranga yaco, hari ibintu vyinshi vyotegerezwa gukorwa, harimwo gukomeza ubutunzi bw'igihugu, kugabanya ibibazo vya politike n'umutekano, hamwe no kugenzura neza ibijanye n'ifaranga n'ubudandaji mpuzamakungu.

1. **Impamvu za Politiki:** Mu Burundi, abatavuga rumwe na leta, abanyapolitiki batavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi, abanyamakuru, n'abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bakunze guhura n'ibibazo byo gutotezwa, gufungwa mu buryo butemewe n'amateko, inyuruzwa, n'iyicwa. Ibi bikorwa bikunze kugamije gucecekesha no gutera ubwoba abanenga ubutegetsi cyangwa abafite ibitekerezo bitandukanye n'ibya leta.

2. **Impamvu z'Amoko:** Amateka y'u Burundi agaragaza ko habayeho ubwicanyi n'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku moko, cyane cyane hagati y'Abahutu n'Abatutsi. Nubwo ibihe by'intambara z'amoko bisa n'ibyarangiye, hari igihe ibikorwa by'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku moko bikigaragara, bikaba byagira uruhare mu nyuruzwa n'iyicwa ry'abantu.

3. **Ubutabera Bucagase:** Ubutabera mu Burundi bwakunze kunengwa kuba budakora neza, aho abakoze ibyaha by'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku mpamvu za politiki cyangwa amoko badahabwa ibihano bikwiye. Ibi bituma habaho umuco wo kudahana, aho abantu bamwe bumva ko bashobora gukora ibyaha nk'ibi ntibakurikiranwe.

4. **Umutekano Muke:** U Burundi bwahuye n'ibibazo by'umutekano muke mu bihe bitandukanye, aho imitwe yitwaje intwaro, imitwe y'abagizi ba nabi, n'izindi nzego zishobora kuba zarakoze ibikorwa by'inyuruzwa n'iyicwa ry'abantu mu rwego rwo guhungabanya umutekano w'igihugu cyangwa mu rwego rw'ibikorwa byabo bya gisirikare cyangwa bya politiki.

5. **Ibibazo by'Ubukungu n'Imibereho:** Uburundi ni kimwe mu bihugu bikennye cyane ku isi, aho ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho mibi bishobora gutuma habaho umutekano muke, bigatuma bamwe mu baturage bashobora kujya mu bikorwa by'urugomo cyangwa ibyaha byo kubaho.

Impamvu twahevye gukoresha imiti kama (cyangwa imiti gakondo) mu buryo bwagutse, ahubwo tukimakaza imiti mishya y'ubuvuzi bwa kijyambere, ni ingaruka y'impinduka zinyuranye mu mibereho y'abantu, iterambere ry'ubumenyi n'ikoranabuhanga, hamwe n'ihindagurika ry'imyumvire ku bijyanye n'ubuzima n'ubuvuzi. Dore impamvu zimwe na zimwe z'ingenzi:

1. **Iterambere ry'Ubumenyi n'Ikoranabuhanga**: Ubumenyi mu by'ubuvuzi bwateye imbere cyane mu kinyejana cya 20, bituma habaho ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku miti n'uburyo bwo kuvura. Ibi byatumye haboneka imiti mishya ifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu buryo bwizewe kurushaho, ifite ibipimo byizewe by'ingano n'uburyo bwo gukoresha, hamwe n'ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku ngaruka zayo.

2. **Ubwoko bw'Indwara**: Indwara zihinduka mu gihe, kandi izo imiti kama yavuraga neza mu bihe byashize zishobora kuba zitakiri zimwe mu mbogamizi zikomeye z'ubuzima muri iki gihe. Ubu, duhanganye n'indwara z'ibyorezo nk'agakoko gatera SIDA, kanseri, indwara z'umutima, n'izindi zisaba ubuvuzi bugezweho n'ubushakashatsi bwimbitse.

3. **Ubwizerwe n'Umutekano**: Imwe mu mbogamizi zikomeye z'imiti kama ni ukutagira ubuziranenge buhagije n'ubwizerwe mu ngano n'uburyo bwo gukoresha. Imwe mu miti gakondo ishobora kuba irimo uburozi cyangwa ingaruka mbi zidakwiye. Mu gihe imiti mishya y'ubuvuzi bwa kijyambere ikorerwa mu bigo byemewe, igapimwa kandi igasuzumwa mu buryo buhagije mbere yo kwemererwa gukoreshwa.

4. **Ubuvuzi Bwemewe n'Amategeko**: Amategeko y'ubuzima n'ubuvuzi mu bihugu byinshi ashyigikira ubuvuzi bwa kijyambere, butanga amabwiriza akomeye ku bijyanye n'ubushakashatsi, umutekano, n'ubuziranenge bw'imiti. Ibi bituma imiti mishya igira inzira ndende yo kunyuramo mbere yo kwemererwa, bikarinda abarwayi ingaruka zishobora guterwa n'imiti idafite ubuziranenge.

5. **Uburezi n'Ubukangurambaga**: Mu bihe bya none, abantu benshi bafite ubumenyi n'ubushobozi bwo kugera ku makuru ajyanye n'ubuzima n'ubuvuzi. Ibi bituma benshi bahitamo ubuvuzi bwa kijyambere bushingiye ku bushakashatsi n'ibimenyetso bya siyansi.

Uburundi, n'ubwo bufise ibiyaga vyinshi n'ibindi bisanzwe vy'umwimbu w'amazi, buracafise ingorane zikomeye zijanye n'ugutanga umuyagankuba uhagije ku banyagihugu baco. Izi ngorane ziterwa n'impamvu zitandukanye zirimo:

1. **Ibikorwa remezo bidakwiye**: Uburundi buracari inyuma mu bijanye n'ibikorwa remezo vy'umuyagankuba. Ibikorwa remezo vy'umuyagankuba bisaba ishoramari rinini kandi rirambye, kandi Uburundi buracafise ingorane zijanye n'ubukene bw'uburyo bwo gushora imari muri ivyo bikorwa.

2. **Ubukene bw'ishoramari**: Ishoramari mu gisata c'umuyagankuba rirakenewe cane kugira ngo haboneke umuyagankuba uhagije. Uburundi buracakeneye abashoramari b'imbere mu gihugu n'abo hanze yaco kugira ngo bashore imari mu bikorwa vy'umuyagankuba.

3. **Ihindagurika ry'ibihe**: Ihindagurika ry'ibihe riragira ingaruka mbi ku bisanzwe vy'umwimbu w'amazi mu Burundi, bigatuma ubushobozi bwo gukora umuyagankuba buva mu mazi bugabanuka. Ibi bishobora gutuma ibiyaga n'inzuzi bitanga amazi make yo gukoresha mu guhingura umuyagankuba.

4. **Ubwinshi bw'abanyagihugu n'iterambere ry'igihugu**: Uko igihugu kirushiriza gutera imbere n'uko abanyagihugu barushiriza kwiyongera, ni ko n'ibisabwa mu bijanye n'umuyagankuba birushiriza kwiyongera. Uburundi bufise ibice binini vy'abanyagihugu batarashikirwa n'umuyagankuba, bigatuma haba umwitwarariko mu gutanga umuyagankuba uhagije.

5. **Gutunganya neza umuyagankuba**: Hariho kandi ikibazo co gutunganya neza umuyagankuba uhari, harimwo no gukwiragiza umuyagankuba mu bice bitandukanye by'igihugu. Ibi bisaba ibikorwa remezo vyiza n'ubuhinga bwo gukwirakwiza umuyagankuba.

Mu gushira mu ngiro ingamba zo gukemura izi ngorane, harakenewe ishoramari rikomeye mu bikorwa remezo, gukoresha neza ibisanzwe vy'umwimbu w'amazi, no guteza imbere ubuhinga bushasha mu guhingura umuyagankuba. Hariho kandi amahirwe yo gukoresha ubundi buryo bw'umuyagankuba butari ubwo mu mazi, nka solar na biogas, kugira ngo Uburundi bushobore guhangana n'iki kibazo c'umuyagankuba.

5. **Impamvu z'ubukungu:** Gushyingiranwa n'abagore baturutse mu miryango ikomeye cyangwa mu turere dutandukanye byashoboraga kandi kuba uburyo bwo gukomeza ubukungu bw'ubwami. Bishobora kuba byarafashije mu gukwirakwiza umutungo, guhuza ubutaka, cyangwa gukomeza ubucuruzi n'ubuhahirane hagati y'uturere dutandukanye.

Mu gusoza, impamvu z'umwami kugira abagore mu turere twinshi tw'igihugu ziratandukanye kandi zishingiye ku mateka, umuco, n'imibereho y'ibyo bihe. Ni ingenzi kandi kuzirikana ko ibi byakorwaga mu buryo buhuje n'umuco n'imigenzo y'icyo gihe, nubwo muri iki gihe bishobora kutumvikana cyangwa kutakirwa neza mu mico imwe n'imwe.

prompting_state.prompt: Amasezerano yo kwakwa akarere ka Bugufi yasinyiwe na ba nde? Ryari? Kubera iki?

Kirundi.text:
Amasezerano yo kwakwa akarere ka Bugufi (Treaty of Trianon) yasinyiwe ku itariki ya 4 Kamena 1920 hagati y'ibihugu by'ibihangange byari byaratsinze mu Ntambara ya Mbere y'Isi (Allied Powers) n'igihugu cya Hongiriya. Aya masezerano yari agamije gusubiza ibibazo by'imbibi n'ubusugire bw'ibihugu byari byaravutse cyangwa byari byarongerewe ubutaka nyuma y'isenyuka ry'Ubwami bwa Austro-Hungariya, bwari bumaze gutsindwa mu Ntambara ya Mbere y'Isi.

Aya masezerano yasinyiwe i Trianon, mu Bufaransa, kandi yari afite ingaruka zikomeye ku gihugu cya Hongiriya. Hongiriya yatakaje igice kinini cy'ubutaka bwayo, hafi 72% by'ubutaka bwayo bwariho mbere y'intambara, ndetse n'abaturage bagera kuri 64% bari batuye muri ubwo butaka. Ibi byatumye Hongiriya itakaza ibice byinshi byari bifite ubukungu n'umuco by'ingenzi, birimo na Transylvania yahawe Romania, Slovakia na Ruthenia yahawe Czechoslovakia, Burasirazuba bwa Slovenia, Croatia, na Vojvodina byahawe Serbiya (icyo gihe yari igize igice cya Yugoslavia), n'ibindi bice byahawe Austria na Romania.

Impamvu y'aya masezerano yari ukugerageza gushyiraho amahoro arambye mu karere k'Uburayi bwo hagati nyuma y'isenyuka ry'Ubwami bwa Austro-Hungariya, no gukemura ibibazo by'ubusugire bw'ibihugu byari bishya cyangwa byari byarongerewe ubutaka. Icyakora, ingaruka zayo ziremereye ku gihugu cya Hongiriya zatumye habaho umujinya n'akababaro mu baturage, ndetse n'ibibazo by'ubukungu n'umutekano muri ako karere k'Uburayi mu myaka yakurikiyeho.

prompting_state.prompt: Umugabo yemeye kwigura umwami Mwezi Gisabo yitwa gute? Hari habaye iki?

Kirundi.text:
Umugabo wemeye kwigura Umwami Mwezi Gisabo yitwa Ntare Rugamba. Ibi byabaye mu gihe cy'ingoma ya Mwezi Gisabo, umwami wa nyuma w'ingoma ya Burundi mbere y'uko igitugu cy'abakoloni gitangira. Ntare Rugamba yari umutware w'ingabo z'umwami, kandi yari azwiho ubutwari n'ubuhanga mu bya gisirikare.

Igikorwa cyo kwigura cyabaye mu gihe cy'intambara yahuje u Burundi n'abakoloni b'Abadage. Mu mwaka wa 1903, Abadage bashatse gufata Umwami Mwezi Gisabo ngo bamuce intege, bityo bamufatira mu murwa mukuru w'ubwami, Usumbura (ubu ni Bujumbura). Mwezi Gisabo yari afite amakenga ko ashobora gufatwa n'Abadage, bityo agahitamo kwihisha. Ntare Rugamba, nk'umwe mu bagabo be b'inkoramutima, yemeye kwigura umwami, yiyambika imyambaro y'umwami kugira ngo Abadage bamwitiranye na Mwezi Gisabo. Ibi byahaye umwami umwanya wo guhunga.

Nubwo Ntare Rugamba yagerageje kwigura umwami, Abadage baje kumenya ko batwaye umuntu utari Mwezi Gisabo nyawe. Nyuma yaho, Mwezi Gisabo yaje gufatwa n'Abadage mu kindi gikorwa cyabo cyo kumuhiga. Uyu mwami yaje gushyira umukono ku masezerano y'ubukoloni mu 1903, aho u Burundi bwabaye igice cy'ubukoloni bw'Abadage, nyuma bukaza kugengwa n'Ababiligi nyuma y'Intambara ya Mbere y'Isi.

Igikorwa cya Ntare Rugamba cyo kwigura umwami kigaragaza ubwitange n'ubudahemuka bw'abari hafi y'umwami, ndetse n'uburyo abami b'u Burundi bari bafite abantu b'ingenzi babashyigikiye mu bihe bikomeye.
